'''Drive shafts''' were components used in building [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[HAVw A6 Juggernaut/Legends|juggernauts]]. One juggernaut, [[Juggernaut-11]], was stationed on [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]] where an [[Imperial machinist]] found the drive shaft snapped.

